    <h2 {...{
      "id": "access-the-system"
    }}>{`Access the system`}</h2>
    <p>{`Once everything is configured correctly your cluster and DNS, you should be able to setup the Factory application. By navigating to the Factory domain `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`factory.domain.com`}</inlineCode>{` in your browser you will see the Factory login page showing up.`}</p>
